# Google Sheets MCP

Project: `google-sheets-mcp/`

## Auth modes

| `GOOGLE_AUTH_MODE` | Use case |
|--------------------|----------|
| `oauth` | User's own Drive (run `npm run auth` first) |
| `service_account` | Shared/team sheets (share with SA email) |
| `auto` | OAuth token if present, else service account |

## OAuth one-time login

```bash
export GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_PATH=/path/to/oauth-client.json
cd google-sheets-mcp && npm run auth
```

Redirect URI in Google Cloud: `http://127.0.0.1:38473/oauth2callback`

## Cursor: both accounts

Register two servers with different names — `google-sheets` (oauth) and `google-sheets-sa` (service_account). Same binary, different `env`.

Rebuild: `cd google-sheets-mcp && npm run build`
